Cudurka fayraska ah waxaa si ku meel gaar ah loo ogaan karaa calaamadaha ugu horreeya, in kasta oo xaqiijinta ugu dambeysa ay tahay in lagu sameeyo tijaabooyin taban oo ka mid ah falcelinta sanka ee polymerase-CoV (rRT-PCR) ee walxaha la soo saaray ama CT-ga.
Daraasad isbarbardhig ah oo ka dhacday falcelinta polymerase ee Wuhan ayaa muujisay in polymerase ka badan falcelinta polymerase, iyadoo astaamaha muuqaalkeeda badan ay ku xiran yihiin cudurka sanbabada iyo nidaamyada kale ee cudurka, inkasta oo aan la hubin.
Laga soo bilaabo Maarso 2020, College of Radiology ee Mareykanka ayaa soo jeedisay in CT-ga aan loo isticmaalin in lagu ogaado ama aan loo isticmaalin doorashada koowaad ee baaritaanka COVID-19.
