Madaxweynaha Iran Hassan Rouhani ayaa warqad shacab ah u diray hoggaamiyeyaasha adduunka oo uu codsanayay caawimaad 14 March 2020, isagoo sheegay in dalkiisa uu ku dhibtoonayo la dagaalanka cudurka faafa sababtuna tahay la'aanta xuquuqda suuqa caalamiga ah ee ka dhalatay cunaqabateynta Mareykanka ee Iran. Faafida cudurka ayaa u horseeday Mareykanka inuu si deg deg ah u qaado go'aano muhiim ah oo ku saabsan hirgelinta mabaadi'da bulshada ee guud ahaan loo isticmaalo dalal kale, oo ay ku jiraan nidaamyada daryeelka caafimaadka ee daryeelka caafimaadka, daryeelka caafimaadka carruurta, sharci dejinta qoysaska leh mushaharka sare iyo bixinta daryeelka caafimaadka ee dadweynaha.
Falanqeeyayaasha siyaasadda ayaa filayay inay saameyn xun ku yeelan karto suurtagalnimada Donald Trump inuu dib u doorto doorashada madaxtinimada ee 2020. Xiriirka diblomaasiyadeed ee u dhexeeya Japan iyo South Korea ayaa sii xanaaqaya masiibada.
