Gacmaha ballaaran waa tusaale kale oo ololeyaal wacyiga ah oo isku dayaya in la gaaro isbeddel ku yimaada anshax. Iyada oo ay ka dhalatay faafitaanka cudurka faafa ee 2019-20, UNICEF waxay kor u qaadday ansixinta calaamadaha dareenka ee gacmaha lagu dhaqdo.
