Maareynta khatarta ee kooxda, marka lagu daro tallaabooyinka ka hortagga cudurka faafa ee aasaasiga ah, waxaa ka mid ah dabaysha soo baxa ee ku saleysan qaab dabayl oo tayo sare leh, ka hortagga qanjirka, iyo qalabka difaaca ee la heli karo marka la kulmo dadka qaba COVID-19.
