Istaraatiijiyada saddexaad waa tallaalka difaaca nukliyeerka (DNA ama RNA, oo ah farsamooyinka cusub ee loo yaqaan 'vaccine-setting techniques' ee loo yaqaan 'vaccine-setting techniques').
Tijaabada tallaalka ee ka soo jeeda mid ka mid ah istaraatiijiyadahaas ayaa la tijaabi doonaa si loo hubiyo badbaadada iyo waxtarka. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, tijaabada ugu horreysa ee tallaalka ayaa la bilaabay afar mutadawiciin ah oo ku sugan Seattle.
Tallaalka ayaa leh geeno aan ka soo horjeedin fayraska cudurka. Kordhinta ku tiirsan antigen ayaa lagu soo bandhigay inay tahay caqabad suurtagal ah oo loogu talagalay horumarinta tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin waa mid muran leh.
In ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad oo shaqsiyeed oo firfircoon ayaa socda sida April 2020.
Toddoba tijaabo ayaa lagu qiimeeyay daaweyn diyaar u ah cudurka qanjirka 'cranial cancer', oo ay ku jiraan afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan isugeynta, chlorogeny ama chlorogeny.
Daawooyinka loo yaqaan 'recycled antiviral drugs' ayaa inta badan gacan ka geystay cilmi baarista Shiinaha, iyadoo la soo saaray sagaal tijaabo oo marxaladood oo III ah oo Remdesivir ah oo laga sameeyay dalal badan, sida lagu sheegay warbixin la soo dhaafay bishii April.
Dib u eegis ku saabsan horumarka bukaanka ee tallaalka COVID-19 iyo daawooyinka la soo bandhigay ayaa la soo saaray, ilaa iyo bishii Abriil 2020. Daawooyin badan oo cusub oo ka hortagga fayraska ayaa lagu qiimeynayaa daaweynta COVID-19, Remdesivir, Chloroquine iyo Hydroxychloroquine, Lopinavir/Ritonavir iyo Lopinavir/Ritonavir oo lagu daray Interferon beta.
